":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:34:59.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"484612f45073b618d7bbfe6ffc8f430bd8d8d902","tid":1741482,"uid":150370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:40:24.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"14cbafdc8685ca3f81e8e6dcddff88de97511364","tid":1741482,"uid":150370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c21dc39f478478fcdde4d8b4bd13524a76e1a2","tid":1741482,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:15:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鄭文傑單野有冇人煲大煲上國際不停煲? 幾千張photo點黎? 係唔係林鄭俾過去?<br />\n一地兩檢既後果(呢個區選都可以用黎屌當日支持一地兩檢既人)<br />\n<br />\n區選唔好唔投,你點睇區選都好,只要係俾建制贏(只係贏就夠,唔駛大贏)<br />\n林鄭同POPO直頭可以大條道理出機關槍,所以一定要投,要正正經經咁投<br />\n<br />\n有機會,順手&quot;教&quot;下藍絲投票<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tod5ssj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftod5ssj.jpg&h=68ec4a3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac449acd44deab0dbdcc8e754eecc115eb6fa78d","tid":1741482,"uid":150370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36b8b11715bef2b157cce65f100acb967fe22c57","tid":1741482,"uid":257736,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:27:17.000Z","msg":"你不是在示威中揮旗嗎？<br />\n<br />\n係咪王婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:18:41.000Z","msg":"8.11 後未露面　王婆婆透露深圳被捕　正取保候審　籲港人代她加油<br />\n【報道全文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XH1UZT】\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XH1UZT%E3%80%91&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=39bc4caa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XH1UZT】</a><br />\n<br />\n過去經常在抗爭現場揮舞港英旗的「王婆婆」王鳳瑤，自今年 8 月 11 日在太古港鐵站被帶走後不知去向。《立場新聞》今午接獲王婆婆訊息，她透露自己正在深圳取保候審，手上的選票，已化為廢紙，呼籲港人今日代她加油，包括要監票留守。王婆婆在電郵中未有交待因何事被捕。《立場新聞》正就事件向保安局查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}